\par\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\ltrch\loch \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Well done,\u8221\'94 the Guide complimented him. \u8220\'93Your previous exposure to the breathing technique and the pre-system meditation techniques seems to have served you well.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Thanks.\u8221\'94 Marcus replied absently as he thought back over his various skill evolutions. He was noticing a pattern. \u8220\'93Do all Tier 1 skills evolve to Tier 2 at level ten?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93No. However a skill must reach a minimum of level of ten times their tier before they can be evolved. The actual evolution is a result of your comprehension of the skill or technique you are using. Tier 1 skills, however, are the simplest to learn and evolve, so they only rarely progress much past Level 10 before evolving to the next Tier. As you get into higher Tier skills, that will reach a point where it is extremely rare to see a skill immediately evolve.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He nodded along with her explanation, feeling like it made perfect sense. As a skill grew in complexity and potential applications, it would get harder to advance them. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ah, thanks for the clarification. I\u8217\'92ve just been doing well with comprehension and these are low tier skills. Got it.\u8221\'94 }
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93If you mean you are in the lower tiers of these skill, then you are correct.\u8221\'94 The Guide countered his statement. \u8220\'93If you mean these are of limited value, then you are grossly incorrect. Both Mana Control and Meditation are regarded as essential skills throughout the Multiverse for anyone pursuing a path involving magic.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf4 [While it was obvious why Mana Control would be considered essential, Marcus considered his meditation for a while, pondering her words and why it might be so highly regarded. After a short while, the understanding hit home.]}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93It\u8217\'92s the ability to study mana flows so deeply while meditating, isn\u8217\'92t it? That makes it easier to grasp concepts related to mana.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes.\u8221\'94 The Guide answered with a nod. \u8220\'93As you sink into deeper states of meditation, your ability to perceive mana interactions and even fundamental concepts grows proportionately.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 He nodded again, grasping the obvious implications. \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I guess those hermits on remote mountaintops meditating on the universe and seeking enlightenment were on the right path,\u8221\'94 he joked.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Essentially yes. Though they lacked techniques to truly achieve their goals without the System.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Marcus rolled his eyes internally as he considered the Guide\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s hit and miss ability to recognize his attempts at humor. Then he checked the time remaining before the next evaluation would begin.}
