\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 So it had taken around an hour and a half for him to learn meditation, which was a lot longer than it had seemed at the time, but then time was weird that way. Which immediately got him wondering\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85 \u8220\'93Time is a concept, right?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Yes.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93So you can use mana to manipulate Time?\u8221\'94 Holy shit, that was a cool idea.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93With sufficient understanding of the concept, yes.\u8221\'94 The Guide replied. \u8220\'93Doing so is called Chronomancy and is one of the more complex and esoteric branches of magical study.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 That\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8230\'85 was\u8230\'85 awesome. And then his rational brain prodded him again. He\u8217\'92d spent the time he was going to use to experiment with mana learning meditation, and he did not feel like 40 minutes was enough time to do anything worthwhile in that regard. So instead, he turned to one last set of questions he had.}
